| commenting, to make the data accessible remove the comment characters:

| nta - Na-talc
| tap - talc-pyrophyllite
| tan - talc-phlogopite

| Additionally the "fact" (ferro-actinolite) endmember has been renamed 
| "ftr" to maintain consistency with ds5 data files.

| data from other sources (HSC, SUPCRT, etc) has been added at the end of this
| file. JADC, January 29, 2026

begin_standard_variables |<= name (<9 characters), reference value, tolerance
